### Repository Layer

#### [NEW] backend/src/repositories/site.repository.ts

`SiteRepository` class with methods:

| Method | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| `findAll(orgId, skip, limit, filters)` | Paginated list with filters, includes manager + technician count |
