| `update(siteId, data, orgId)` | Update site fields |
| `delete(siteId, orgId, force)` | Soft/hard delete |
| `assignTechnician(siteId, userId)` | Update a user's `site_id` to assign them to the site |
| `removeTechnician(userId)` | Nullify a user's `site_id` to remove them from the site |

