### Service Layer

#### [NEW] backend/src/services/site.service.ts

`SiteService` class with business logic:

| Method | Key Business Rules |
|--------|-------------------|
| `create()` | Validate unique name per org; validate `manager_id` is a facility_manager role; check FM not already assigned to another site |
| `getAll()` | Paginated list, supports `search`, `is_active` filters |
| `getById()` | Get with manager + technicians |
| `update()` | Re-validate name uniqueness if changed; re-validate FM assignment if changed |
| `delete()` | Soft-delete first, then hard-delete on second call |
| `assignManager()` | Assign/unassign a Facility Manager; enforce 1:1 constraint |
| `assignTechnician()` | Validate user ID exists, has technician role, and update their `site_id` |
| `removeTechnician()` | Remove technician from site by clearing `site_id` |

